 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621640}, {"id": 342812, "content": "习惯性的删掉输入法app，再重新下载，就不会有记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555854}, {"id": 342815, "content": "jb=加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978756}, {"id": 344864, "content": "陈--颖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607376}, {"id": 342817, "content": "输入H是第一个是他的名字，输入X是第一个是对前任的爱称。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407519}, {"id": 342819, "content": "发现好多都是前任名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801006}, {"id": 344868, "content": "记住了一个不愿提起的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655179}, {"id": 342821, "content": "打兴趣总是蹦出性趣emmmm", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485318}, {"id": 342823, "content": "经常出现和前任的对话、昵称之类的，于是我换了手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183067}, {"id": 342824, "content": "我哭了", "image": "img/option/option/20190506141249NGsiyRAZ0nc5rDH7", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649321}, {"id": 342825, "content": "打出：没有 系统默认首选：钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614168}, {"id": 342827, "content": "昨天有人问我穿的热不热，我回答一句惹。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 342829, "content": "当然是出柜啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144988}, {"id": 342832, "content": "疏乳法本身 （微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294190}, {"id": 342833, "content": "想给甲方说“我去做提纲”，打出了“我去做提肛”……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957686}, {"id": 342834, "content": "自己的名字全拼是洗衣机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481783}, {"id": 342835, "content": "有没有试着打评论内容的😆", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586582}, {"id": 342836, "content": "都在截图里了", "image": "img/option/option/201905061545257aheoYliTpSPD4u6.png", "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188884}, {"id": 342838, "content": "iPhone 想连续打很多个符号的时候.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 342839, "content": "我长得不好看😂😂😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449386}, {"id": 342840, "content": "分手小半年了，每次打wx都会跳出她的名字，曾经熟悉的字眼如今却深深刺痛我的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647625}, {"id": 342841, "content": "刚打出拜拜，自动出来我之前忘不掉的那个男孩的名字………", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598447}, {"id": 343609, "content": "首充饭卡的时候名字最后一个输入法找不到，只能省略掉那个字将就了π_π", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625789}, {"id": 342842, "content": "想切换日语输入法的时候要从三遍中文切2遍韩文再到日文再切中文", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596021}, {"id": 342843, "content": "偷人打就没对过🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643907}, {"id": 343102, "content": "要是真对我了解我还没话说了，关键是新机才上手时的联想词语emmmmmm", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026129}, {"id": 343616, "content": "在公司群里面被领导@，提交的oa流程，“暖场活动”打成了“暖床活动”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830914}, {"id": 343375, "content": "看到委屈却憋着不哭的人(´;︵;`)，我心都碎了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548340}, {"id": 342864, "content": "输入fb...第一选项：番号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967398}, {"id": 342870, "content": "“我喜欢/爱/和/…【自动输入对方名称】”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612475}, {"id": 342880, "content": "做陈列方案的时候，用九宫格输入chenl没有出现陈列，只是关联到了人名", "image": "img/option/option/20190506183311IguYzSPEJoHwWsAb.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006720}, {"id": 343136, "content": "Gboard 词汇甚是匮乏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641200}, {"id": 342881, "content": "我老公输入“老婆”=“老宋”，然后我一直问他老宋是不是三……😓", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447582}, {"id": 342882, "content": "输入验证码总是给我纠正成单词🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648592}, {"id": 342883, "content": "没有故事，也没有事故，一切正常。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639314}, {"id": 342886, "content": "输入法的联想和猜测功能，让手速快眼睛慢的我遭遇很多尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 342887, "content": "每次拼音输入想选择第一个出现的字的时候总是不小心按到第二个字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411332}, {"id": 342888, "content": "抵制国内花里胡哨的输入法。微软的输入法，前两次还能根据已输入的联想，第三次就失忆了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649440}]}